text: The Baltimore Bays were a professional soccer team based in Baltimore, Maryland from 1967 to 1969. Baltimore Bays may also refer to: *Baltimore Bays (1972–73); member of the American Soccer League from 1972 to 1973 *Baltimore Bays (1993–98); member of United States International Soccer League from 1993 to 1998 *Maryland Bays; member of the American Soccer League/American Professional Soccer League from 1988 to 1991
title: Baltimore Bays (disambiguation)
